My art.

630
00:55:30,718 --> 00:55:34,603
But sometimes, if I really want

631
00:55:34,638 --> 00:55:37,389
that good, full feeling...

632
00:55:55,409 --> 00:55:57,910
<i>He wasn't just
building the finest hotel.</i>

633
00:55:57,995 --> 00:55:59,211
<i>Los Angeles had ever seen.</i>

634
00:56:00,831 --> 00:56:03,931
<i>It was a perfectly designed</i>
<i>torture chamber.</i>

635
00:56:04,051 --> 00:56:06,802
<i>An engineered alibi.</i>

636
00:56:06,837 --> 00:56:09,421
<i>Secret chutes and rooms</i>

637
00:56:09,506 --> 00:56:11,234
<i>to hide and dispose</i>
