00:56:20,684 --> 00:56:23,068
<i>so they could mute the screams.</i>

641
00:56:23,153 --> 00:56:24,519
<i>People walked in,</i>

642
00:56:24,605 --> 00:56:26,772
<i>just vanished.</i>

643
00:56:26,867 --> 00:56:28,834
<i>"No body, no crime,"</i>
<i>he would say.</i>

644
00:56:28,859 --> 00:56:32,205
No, no.

